          <p class="ba-sub">Where you land in your first 30 days.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>One engine. Everything connected.</h4>
              <p>Keyword research, drafting, scoring, publishing, GBP, social, reviews — running from one dashboard, in real time.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
