            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>$99/month. 30+ articles delivered.</h4>
              <p>One platform replaces your agency, your freelancers, and your tool stack. Same outcome — 35× cheaper.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Cited by every AI search engine</h4>
              <p>Articles structured so ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, Claude, and Copilot quote you as the source. New traffic channel, zero extra work.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
